Author: Cryptoby
Title: [ANN][ICO] SWAY: SkyWay – New Generation of Transport System
Body: Attention!!! Attention!!!   This Coin isn't a coin from the Skyway Company! It is a scammer coin and from a counterfeiter!  I'm a partner and investor of the very interesting Project named „Skyway“. I saw this coin offering and the website related to it and thought immediatelly there must be something wrong. So I contacted the real Skyway Company and asked them about this ICO, the SWAY Coin and the website skywayico.com. The answer was that this is a scammer!  The Skyway Company and the Project are both real and very promising (as many of you could see in the video) but they don't have any cryptocoin! They sell shares in a crowdfunding campain. The video is from the real Skyway Company (but copied and published under the name „Skyway ICO“ which belongs to the deceiver).  Nevertheless you can invest into the very interesting Skyway project. I think it has a very big future and everyone who invests now, will have big big rewards in similar scale as it is usual in the cryptoworld. If somebody wants to know more about that or wants to invest some money you can do it here:  Register free!!!  You have to register for free and than you can make a deposit and get shares of the company with a good discont at the moment. In the SkywayOffice you can also have a look at their businessplan and other interesting stuff.  They have already reached many goals of their development plan. So I think this is a good sign. At the moment they are realising the EcoTechnopark which is needed for the certification and they are already testing some of their transport systems at the park!  Here is a link to the real Skyway Capital website were you can get more information (it's a link with my ref code, so will get me as contact person if you register).  But please don't be deceived by this SWAY coin! This coin has nothing to do with the real company (which seems to be very good and promising)! If you like this project invest the right way … don't throw your money away!

Author: Cryptoby
Title: [ANN][ICO] SWAY: SkyWay – New Generation of Transport System
Body: You can believe whom ever you want , but this SWAY Coin has nothing to do with the Skyway Project from the inventor Anatoly Yunitskiy. The video, all the links to the articles and many of the information given in the Scammer ICO here on bitcointalk have been copied from this really good and real Project. This fact you can easily verify by yourself ("Skyway ICO" was announced here at July 08, 2017 with many copied material and links to reports describing the real Project Skyway. In contrast to this there is the Company Skyway Capital (or correct name is called FIRST SKYWAY INVEST GROUP LIMITED) which was incorporated in the year 2014 with Mr Evgenii Kudriashov as director under the Company number 09320759). If you don't believe me that Skyway has nothing to do with this ICO and even not anyhing to do with cryptocurrency than you are free to ask their support about that, if you want  ... sure the development of the right project is worth to watching ... it's very promising in my opinion ... but if you want to invest please do it really into the original project and not into a scammer where you don't get what you want and what was promised to you ...  For all who are interested to invest, you can do it here after your registration (you will also find many documents (e.g. the business plan) and further information in your account under the button "Investors" and than "Documents"). Author: skyway
Title: [ANN][ICO] SWAY: SkyWay – New Generation of Transport System
Body: Hello,  Please let me explain our Holding structure:  - We have an R&D center in Belarus, where you can see first SkyWay transport samples. General Director and Constructor of this center is Anatoly Unitsky;  - We have several croudfunding companies, like SkyWay ICO, SkyWay Capital, SkyWay Invest Goup (SWIG) and some others. They find investors to continue project development, but using different ways;  - SkyWay Holding Gmbh - our head organization, located in Austria. It's easy to find it in public records. This holding structure controls all stages of development, production, marketing and investments in SkyWay Project.  That's why SkyWay ICO and Skyway Capital has the same product, but use different ways to promote it.  Hope, we've answered your question.

Author: RaLight
Title: [ANN][ICO] SWAY: SkyWay – New Generation of Transport System
Body: LT Gerbiami naudotojai, saugokitės sukčių!  Forume pristatyta svetainė neturi nieko bendro su Anatolijaus Eduardovičiaus Junitskio kuriamu styginiu transportu. Visa pateikta svetainėje medžiaga yra paimta iš oficialių svetainių ir naudojama pinigams išvilioti. Pabrėžiama, jog oficialūs SkyWay technologijos kūrėjai neplatina jokių monetų, o per SkyWay Capital fondą tinklinio marketingo pagrindu platina Euroasian Rail Skyway Systems Holding  Limited akcijas, kurias gali įsigyti kiekvienas norintis. Euroasian Rail Skyway Systems Holding Limited yra intelektinės nuosavybės savininkė, todėl labai palanku šiuo metu į ją investuoti, nes sparčiai vystomas EkoTechnoParkas, kuriame kuriamas, bandomas ir sretifikuojamas styginis transportas. Per EkoFest 2017 renginį EkoTechnoParke jau viešai pristatytos veikiančios trys transporto rūšys: miesto lengvoji, miesto ir krovininė.  Šaltiniai: autoriaus svetainė (SkyWay technology author official page): RU - http://yunitskiy.com/, EN - http://yunitskiy.com/author/english.htm Pagrindinės įmonės svetainė (Head company site): rsw-systems.com SkyWay Capital fondo oficiali svetainė (SkyWay Capital fund official site): https://skyway.capital  Sėkmės investuojant!

Author: fikihafana
Title: [ANN][ICO] SWAY: SkyWay – New Generation of Transport System
Body: I dont trust UK Registration exactly from https://beta.companieshouse.gov.uk , i dont mean i don't trust UK Country. According my experience, many scam project used beta.companieshouse.gov.uk to convince people in their scam. So beta.companieshouse.gov.uk is not warranty a company is legit. I can show you some scam website that used beta.companieshouse.gov.uk , but they are scam.  I saw in your website and this thread have many news from popular website, right?? But i didn't see one of them mention your website especially skywayico.com , they only mention Skyway technology or skyway group not Skywayico. In my opinion Skyway is a general term, so maybe you just used skyway term to get a chance to scam us.

Author: BitMaver
Title: [ANN][ICO] SWAY: SkyWay – New Generation of Transport System
Body: People, be smarter! Don't waste your time and money on this Russian Scam  Here is the original website from which was taken all the information - http://rsw-systems.com/ + press (media) - http://rsw-systems.com/media/press-about + Types of Transport - http://rsw-systems.com/technology  And here is the original YouTube channel - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-NcJ4R7_V8W_3nVkCAswbQ/videos  Scammers copied to their channel only one video - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC238JZZapnQmCLvv093goiQ      Also on the official Facebook page there is a warning about scammers: https://www.facebook.com/SkyWay.official.page/  I quote: "Attention: scammers!  Dear friends! We remind you that lately the activity of swindlers has become more active on the Internet, which, using the SkyWay brand, are engaged in attracting financial resources.  Be vigilant: all relevant and reliable information concerning the SKyWay project is posted only on the official information resources of the developer company - sites rsw-systems.com and sw-tech.by."  Something like that

Author: SashaKh
Title: [ANN][ICO] SWAY: SkyWay – New Generation of Transport System
Body: http://cdn14.skywayico.com/intro.jpg  SKYWAY ICO  WEBSITE | WHITE PAPER | VIDEO | FACEBOOK | TWITTER | SLACK  http://cdn14.skywayico.com/title_1whatis.jpg  SkyWay is an overground high-performance transport technology that has no analogues in the world. This is speed, safety, accessibility, effectivity and environmental friendliness.  SkyWay is a real project with real production since 2015, with more than 200 employees, with test ranges in different countries around the world. All elements of the system are tested thoroughly to ensure that the transport of the future is as safe and reliable as possible.  SkyWay ICO is designed to expand the range of project investors and implement at least the first transport branch in New South Wales, and in the event of a successful ICO, deploy a transport network around the world. If the ICO is successful, SkyWay will become a global transport network by 2025.  http://cdn14.skywayico.com/title_2benefits.jpg  Each buyer of one SWAY token will own one share of class "A" of ERSS HOLDING, which already now has a portfolio of orders at $80 billion USD. At the same time, the global market for the SkyWay transport system is estimated at $400 billion USD.  SWAY tokens will be tied to real production, real contracts with real customers around the world, which will give at least 300% growth during the first months after the release of the token to the world's largest crypto exchanges.  http://cdn14.skywayico.com/title_3docs.jpg  Read our Whitepaper to learn more about our technology and the implementation of the first transport branch in New South Wales. This will allow tokens holders to easily manage them through the default Ethereum Wallet.  The cost of the SWAY token for ICO time is fixed at $1.  SkyWay ICO has a unique bonus system that includes early, personal and collective bonuses, as well as automatic recalculation of all investments at the current exchange rate of the largest exchange Poloniex.  Early Participants Bonus Program motivates to invest in the first stages of the ICO, offering a bonus up to 40%:  http://cdn14.skywayico.com/bonuses1.jpg  Personal Bonus Program motivates participants to invest more to get more bonuses:  http://cdn14.skywayico.com/bonuses2.jpg  All bonuses are summed up.  Investors can make several transactions during ICO. Bonuses will be credited when the transaction is received. For example, you invested 10 BTC, which was equivalent to $25k and received a personal bonus of 15%. If you decide to invest 100 ETH, which is equivalent to $28k, then your total investment (10 BTC + 100 ETH) is equal to $53k and your personal bonuses will be recalculated at 20% value.  Collective Bonus Program http://cdn14.skywayico.com/bonuses3.jpg  $ 10m. Upon reaching this milestone, all investors who have made investments before this point receive a 5% bonus on all their tokens. Achievement of this amount will allow to launch the first line of SkyWay string transport in 2018.  $ 50m. Upon reaching this milestone, all investors who have made investments before this point receive a 10% bonus on all their tokens. The achievement of this amount will allow by 2018 to launch a full-fledged SkyWay communication service in New South Wales and receive orders for $ 250m.  $ 100m. Upon reaching this milestone, all investors who have made investments before this point receive a 15% bonus on all their tokens. Achievement of this amount will allow to launch a full-fledged transport communication between 10 cities of the world, having received orders for $ 1bn by 2020.  $ 250m. Upon reaching this milestone, all investors who have made investments before this point receive a 20% bonus on all their tokens. Achievement of this amount will allow to launch a full-fledged transport communication between 50 cities of the world, and the total portfolio of orders will grow to $ 5bn - $ 15bn by 2020.  $ 500m. Upon reaching this milestone, all investors who have made investments before this moment receive a 25% bonus on all their tokens. Achievement of this amount will already by 2025 launch a full-fledged transport communication between 100 cities around the world, covering the territory of Europe and receiving orders for $ 20bn - $ 60bn.  $ 1000m. At achievement of this boundary ICO is completed early, and all investors without exception receive a bonus of 30% on all their tokens. Achievement of this amount will allow to already by 2025 launch a full-fledged communication between 300 cities of the world, covering Europe, Russia, the UAE and other regions, receiving orders for up to $ 100bn.  Thus, only the combined efforts of investors will help us achieve our goals, and investors will receive additional bonuses.  Conversion of all currencies All investments will be recalculated every day based on the current rates of the largest exchange Poloniex. In addition, if at some point after recalculation of the exchange rate the achievement of a new line of common or collective bonuses will be recorded, this bonus will be added to the investors and will not be canceled any more.  Technical details of SkyWay ICO: Issue: 2,000,000,000 SWAY tokens (including bonus and bounty payments). The total number of SWAY tokens will be limited by the number of tokens actually sold. Dates of the ICO: July 10, 2017 - August 10, 2017. Accepted coins and tokens: BTC, ETH, ETC, LTC, DASH.  After the completion of the ICO, all operations for receiving funds will be closed, and all received investments will be fixed at the current rate of Poloniex.  Further, within 7 days all investors will receive their SWAY tokens taking into account all bonuses and current rates of their invested currencies and tokens. All tokens that will not be sold through this ICO will be burned.  SWAY token will be presented on the largest crypto-exchanges within 1 month after the completion of the ICO.
